Achievements.Name: New Face
Achievements.Description: Create a Custom Player in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Kicked The Six Pack
Achievements.Description: Player kicks six or more goals in one match of AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Aerial Display
Achievements.Description: Player takes 3 or more marks inside the attacking 50m line during one match of AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Bonecrunching Display
Achievements.Description: Perform 10 tackles in a game of AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: So Close Yet So Far
Achievements.Description: After a draw, play through overtime to get a result in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Wicked Win
Achievements.Description: Win by more than 100 points in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Tru Blu Team.

Achievements.Name: Out Of Your League
Achievements.Description: Win a single player match against a higher league team than you in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Winning Attitude
Achievements.Description: Finish a season in career mode with a majority of games won in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Flawless Victory
Achievements.Description: Finish a career season without losing in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Tom Harley All Stars Team.

Achievements.Name: Ton Of Fun
Achievements.Description: End a season with a player kicking 100+ goals in AFL Live 2. Unlocks DC Legends Team.

Achievements.Name: Junior Achiever
Achievements.Description: Win the NAB U/18 Cup in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Williamstown Stadium.

Achievements.Name: A Good Warm Up
Achievements.Description: Win the NAB Cup in any mode in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Tactical Victory
Achievements.Description: Win the TAC Cup in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Port Melbourne Stadium.

Achievements.Name: World Champ
Achievements.Description: Win the International Cup in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Internationals for Single and Online games.

Achievements.Name: Victorian Victors
Achievements.Description: Win the VFL Premiership in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Heritage Guernseys.

Achievements.Name: Best Of The Best
Achievements.Description: Win the AFL Premiership in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Bendigo Stadium.

Achievements.Name: Threepeat
Achievements.Description: Win the AFL Premiership 3 times during in a single career in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Triple Threat
Achievements.Description: Win 3 AFL Premierships in a row in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Whitehorse Stadium.

Achievements.Name: Going The Distance
Achievements.Description: Complete career mode in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Long Hard Road
Achievements.Description: Complete career mode on hard or above manager difficulty in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: TAC Golden Boot
Achievements.Description: Top goal scorer in a TAC season with a player on your team in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: VFL Golden Boot
Achievements.Description: Top goal scorer in VFL season with a player on your team in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: JJ Liston Winner
Achievements.Description: One of your players wins the JJ Liston Medal in a VFL season in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Morrish Medal Winner
Achievements.Description: One of your players wins the Morrish Medal in the TAC Cup in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: McClelland Trophy Winners
Achievements.Description: Finish top of the table in the AFL at the end of the regular season in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Brownlow Medal Legend
Achievements.Description: One of your players wins the Brownlow Medal in AFL Live 2. Unlocks All Stars Team.

Achievements.Name: Coleman Medal Superstar
Achievements.Description: One of your players wins the Coleman Medal in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Victorian Team.

Achievements.Name: Norm Smith Medal Champion
Achievements.Description: One of your players wins the Norm Smith Medal in AFL Live 2. Unlocks TIO Stadium.

Achievements.Name: Ron Evans Medal Ace
Achievements.Description: One of your players wins the NAB Rising Star in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: All Star Superman
Achievements.Description: Reach average stats of 95 on your career player in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Big Ego
Achievements.Description: Read all of the Game Credits in AFL Live 2. Unlocks Big Head Mode.

Achievements.Name: They Are Playing Your Song
Achievements.Description: Win an online game in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: A Win Is A Win
Achievements.Description: Win an online game with more behinds than goals in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: The Numbers Game
Achievements.Description: Win an online game with exactly 20 goals and 13 behinds in AFL Live 2.

Achievements.Name: Footy Fanatic
Achievements.Description: Complete all other achievements in AFL Live 2.
